latestIgtvVideos.title: 2:30 Min Full Body Workout at Home
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here I go with my first workout IGTV, apologies for little wrong dimensions. 

This full body home workout can be done very easily at home and anybody can do it. 

It includes all the body parts-
➡️ Chest✔️
➡️ Back✔️
➡️ Legs✔️
➡️ Shoulder✔️
➡️ Bicep ✔️
➡️ Tricep✔️
➡️ Core✔️

The whole circuit can be done once in a week with 30 seconds of rest after every exercise 💯🏋️

Drink lots of water throughout the day especially when you do heavy and non stop workout ✅

Follow @entrefitbyruchikakhurana for more workout videos 📲
